---
title: Prosciutto, Mozz & Arugula Picnic Sandos Perfectly packable sandwiches for your next adventure!
description: Heading for a hike, the park, the beach? We’ve got your picnic plan right here, and it’s perfectly portable! Toasty baguettes are spread with zesty Italian-seasoned mayo, then layered with luscious prosciutto, creamy sliced mozzarella, juicy tomato, and peppery fresh arugula. Wrap ’em up pro-stye, serve with crunchy cucumbers and sweet orange slices, and you’re ready to roll!
